e=\"text-align: center;\">If you care less about image, you will care more about experiences and memories<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">If you care more about experiences and memories, you will be happier with less<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">If you are happier with less, you\u2019ll never want or need for more<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">The less you want or need for more, the more you will feel free<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&#8211;\u00a0<em><strong><a title=\"The Everyday Minimalist\" href=\"http:\/\/www.everydayminimalist.com\/\" target=\"_blank\">The Everyday Minimalist<\/a><\/strong><\/em><\/p>\n<p>&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8211;<br \/>\n<em>PS: Thanks to <a href=\"http:\/\/fabulouslybroke.com\/\">Fabulously Broke<\/a> for allowing me to re-share this! You&#8217;re an inspiration, my friend.<\/em><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>I saw this over at Everyday Minimalist, and just love it. Thinking of printing it out and putting it on my wall as a reminder&#8230; <\/p>\n<p class=\"more\"><a class=\"more-link\" href=\"https:\/\/budgetsaresexy.vercel.app\/a-minimalist-and-money\/\">Read More<\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":3,"featured_media":21619,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[166,5,158],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-21233","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-get-motivated","category-life","category-minimalism"],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO Premium plugin v24.6 (Yoast SEO v24.5) - https:\/\/yoast.com\/wordpress\/plugins\/seo\/ -->\n<title>A Minimalist And Money | Budgets Are Sexy<\/title>\n<meta name=\"robots\" content=\"index, follow, max-snippet:-1, max-image-preview:large, max-video-preview:-1\" \/>\n<link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"https:\/\/budgetsaresexy.vercel.app\/a-minimalist-and-money\/\" \/>\